Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生 你在聽我說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我在想今晚做什麼菜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 是你讓我告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才來跟你商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東京區域蔓延的對被詛咒的孩子的歧視
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有昨天延珠的身世在學校曝光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因而產生的對今後生活的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的煩惱太過平常 簡直無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這不是在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底 人類為什麼非得殲滅原腸動物不可？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(561,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為它們是人類之敵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上也存在將原腸動物視為淨化地球而出現的神的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.43,0:00:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將它們神聖化的宗教團體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.56,0:00:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用他們的話來說 人類才是耗盡資源 破壞地球的元兇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:01:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那終究只是宣揚人類無用的極端言論吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果原腸動物是神的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(379,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼被詛咒的孩子又算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類和原腸動物之間的信差
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(393,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.63,0:01:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是神的代理人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延珠是人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一個擁有獨立人格和意志的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不是其他什麼別的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此 你不是很清楚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你尚且知道自己來自何方 這已經不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延珠連這都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外圍區的那些被詛咒的孩子 幾乎都是棄兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們不知父母是誰 也不了解外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知被多少人投以輕蔑的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支撐 教育和引導著她們的 又是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不是家人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 你的贊助者有話讓我轉告你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫你偶爾也去學生會室玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是里見先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是藍原同學的班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…從今天早上開始藍原同學來上課了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,400)\pos(205,388)\fsp4\bord0}#03 命運的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:24.75,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,別來學校啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:25.80,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼還在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:26.48,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:27.12,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死的原腸動物 就是因為你們四處屠殺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(314.5,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是人家做的 人家是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延珠 轉學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家…不想…輸…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明已經交了那麼多朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們已經不是你的朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此 我們也必須戰鬥下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里見 已經知道感染源原腸動物的潛伏地點了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(469.5,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要第一個趕去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是這樣 用救護直升機也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我挪用了明年的學費
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是讓別人搶了先 我就得退學了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是原腸動物…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(422.5,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說確實存在把巢編成降落傘的形狀並借此移動的蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能憑藉類似的原理…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 這就是醫生所說的原創能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 延珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降低高度！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮太郎 人家擊敗它了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家擊敗它了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 人家戰鬥了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家保護了學校的同學們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許現在只能繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也理解你不知該何去何從的不安心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還有我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你的珍惜 不會輸給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算世界不接受你 我也會永遠陪伴在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快點回收它 然後回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面到底裝著什麼東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是七星的遺物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一種不祥的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了 里見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到延珠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天童式戰鬥術一型八號「焰火扇」！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你見識一下我的招式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「最強之痛」！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延珠 快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我 蓮太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 延珠逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想殺掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是讓他們和其他民警會合的話 事情會變得麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把工作完成吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太弱了 太弱了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼遺言嗎 即將死亡的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:10:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下地獄去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是里見蓮太郎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一件事希望你做出選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木更小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 里見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…睡了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概睡了整整一天又三個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說你的心臟在手術的最後關頭開始跳動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有放棄生存
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府方面把情報傳達給我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影胤帶走的箱子裡裝有能召喚階段Ⅴ原腸動物的觸媒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(614,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,階段Ⅴ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…毀滅世界的十一隻…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原腸動物從階段Ⅰ開始 經過階段Ⅱ和階段Ⅲ的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(152,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在階段Ⅳ成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,階段Ⅴ則在它的進化範圍之外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從十年前原腸動物誕生時起便存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(377,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比任何原腸動物都巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(421,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絲毫不受錵磁場的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(407,437)\fs21}Varanium
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,階段Ⅴ曾經破壞過數個地區的巨石碑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他原腸動物一同入侵 引發的則是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(301,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「大滅絕」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛭子影胤現在逃到了巨石碑外面的「未探查領域」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始進行召喚階段Ⅴ的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由政府主導的大規模追擊作戰即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不能阻止他們 東京區域就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去嗎 有勝算嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須贏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經做好覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實現在的你需要絕對的靜養
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 木更小姐 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起我還有更需要你去道歉的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從你被抬進來 她就一直守在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮太郎 笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你擔心了 延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖天子大人的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里見先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛭子影胤的追擊作戰已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能參加這次的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於這一點 你自己應該是最清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里見先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別忘了這可不是為了你們做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你好運 里見先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你的贊助者給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要謝就幹出點功績吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我給你的餞別禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGV實驗性藥物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的話最好別用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在失去意識的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我夢見了十年前被你做手術的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你所做的事 無論說什麼都無法被原諒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從那天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從來沒有怨恨過你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以社長的身份命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擊破影胤小比奈組合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止階段Ⅴ的召喚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要為了我比之前努力百倍地工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我會比你更加努力千倍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會阻止他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好險…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 是哪對搭檔使用了爆炸物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮太郎 那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,階段Ⅳ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還記得我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 人家可不認識這個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們究竟是什麼關係給人家說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是一位叫伊熊將監的促進者的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(524,437)\fs21}Promoter
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是起始者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(437,437)\fs21}Initiator
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫千壽夏世
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 人家才不會認可那個女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 只是讓她出去把風 幹嘛那麼不高興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為原因是顯而易見的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.57,0:18:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得我很不可思議嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是具備海豚因子的起始者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(557,437)\fs21}Initiator
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過擁有比普通人更高的智商和記憶力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由頭腦派的你來做後衛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將監則是前鋒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是少見的組合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將監先生連大腦都是肌肉構成的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像後援這種瑣碎的事情他是做不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看看你的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我說不給呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你對被救之事毫無感謝之意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我學到了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在要求回報的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善行便已經墮落了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼在森林裡使用爆炸物？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們發現森林深處有閃爍的燈光 中了陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們以為是民警 便加以接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果那是原腸動物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(482,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們馬上使用了榴彈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就被森林中的原腸動物襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(512,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我與將監先生走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被原腸動物注射體液了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(348,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被注入的體液只有極少的量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有侵蝕率上升的症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心我會原腸動物化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(496,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著 回去以後一定要仔細檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是在擔心我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微有些羨慕延珠小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必延珠小姐沒有殺過人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看她的眼睛就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你殺過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在來這裡的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將遇到的民警搭檔殺掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是將監先生的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說不會將消滅面具混蛋的功勞讓給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:19:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手在顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想很快就會習慣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺人的最恐怖之處就在於習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺人之後 知道自己不會受到懲罰的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人便會逐漸忘卻什麼是罪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾殺過人 所以才這麼說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里見先生有著不可思議的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有著複雜的過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的表情明明那麼溫柔 卻又十分可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在自以為是地胡說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 忘掉剛才的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里見先生說的話是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在很奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明馬上就能想到數十個反駁你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我卻不願否定你所說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的心情…還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 還活著的話就回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您沒事就好 將監先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏世 有個好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到面具混蛋了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他雖然是那種人 也仍然是我的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里見先生你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除將監之外還有十組以上的民警搭檔在進行攻擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只能看到戰鬥的結果 我也要親眼見證到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里見先生 你知道那是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「天梯」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是殺戮兵器的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被掠奪的世代的憎惡的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在所發生的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.95,0:21:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是穩固的復興嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影胤在那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:50.02,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fsp4\be4\bord2}#04  黑色的子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有蓮太郎能拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是其他任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.40,0:23:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有蓮太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Comment: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:51.14,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}ひび割れ　壊れゆく
Comment: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:54.26,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}世界は果てしなく
Comment: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:57.32,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}未知なる創造が
Comment: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:00.35,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}今秩序をなくしてる
Comment: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:03.72,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}重ね合う痛みが
Comment: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:06.82,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}繰り返す現実
Comment: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.75,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}君との毎日が
Comment: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:13.04,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}その闇に身を投げた
Comment: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:16.03,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}指し示した道を
Comment: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:19.24,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}輝かせたいから
Comment: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:25.11,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}黒いこの銃弾が今すべてを撃ちぬく
Comment: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:28.31,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}赤く燃える　その眼差しに
Comment: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:31.37,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}熱く響く　命の鼓動を
Comment: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:36.04,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}強く深く　貫いてゆく　真実を
Comment: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:40.67,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}傷だらけの心を抱いて
Comment: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:43.70,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}ずっと明日を引き寄せるから
Comment: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:48.53,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}この体にすべてを込めて戦うよ
Comment: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:53.74,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}希望を信じて
Comment: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:51.14,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}世界无休止地
Comment: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:54.26,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}变得粉碎
Comment: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:57.32,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}未知的创造
Comment: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:00.35,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}正在破坏着秩序
Comment: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:03.72,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}累积的痛苦
Comment: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:06.82,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}就是重复的现实
Comment: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.75,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}和你度过的每一天
Comment: 0,0:03:09.84,0:03:13.04,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}都投身于这黑暗之中
Comment: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:16.03,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}因为想要照亮
Comment: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:19.24,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}指引的路途
Comment: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:25.11,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}现在我将用这枚黑色的子弹 击穿一切
Comment: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:28.31,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}火红燃烧　为你的眼神
Comment: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:31.37,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}热烈奏响  生命的心跳
Comment: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:36.04,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}强烈深邃地贯穿真实
Comment: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:40.67,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}怀抱布满伤痕的心
Comment: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:43.70,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}因为想要永远拥抱明天
Comment: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:48.53,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}我将身负一切 战斗下去
Comment: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:53.74,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}相信着希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.47,0:22:42.95,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}初めはいつだって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.23,0:22:45.92,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}期待を止められない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.08,0:22:51.40,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}けれどやがて諦めを覚える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:54.30,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}今を守る盾を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.62,0:22:57.29,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}薬莢に詰め込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:23:00.78,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}円く壁を切り取った
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:04.97,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}のぞけば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:12.87,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}終わりが見返してた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:18.87,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}激しい黒に包まれた君の
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.35,0:23:22.12,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}哀情でも心傷でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.19,0:23:24.89,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}全部取り込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.08,0:23:27.78,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}それすら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:30.36,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}僕の糧にしてみせるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.45,0:23:33.14,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}like a lotus
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:34.91,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}だからずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:37.62,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}傍にいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.47,0:22:42.95,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}最初無論何時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.23,0:22:45.92,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}都無法停止期待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.08,0:22:51.40,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}但我最終學會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:54.30,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}將守護現在的盾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.62,0:22:57.29,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}滿滿地裝入彈殼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:23:00.78,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}擊穿高牆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:04.97,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}向外窺探
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:12.87,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}才發現終點正向我回望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:18.87,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}連那包裹在濃烈黑色中的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.35,0:23:22.12,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}你的悲哀與心傷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.19,0:23:24.89,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}我都悉數納入懷中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.08,0:23:27.78,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}即使這些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:30.36,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}我也要將它們變成我的食糧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.45,0:23:33.14,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}like a lotus
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:34.91,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}所以請你一直
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:37.62,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}陪伴在我身邊
